snippet.title: LockYourDoor: Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/3004140/LockYourDoor/

LockYourDoor is a challenging survival horror game for 1-4 players. Your aim is to survive while you search for your friend Darvin. Try your best to stay alive and confront your nightmares. Only the patient and clever will survive.
